   National RC 1983c pp 69 [TEMP, KTMP, RAIN, TEXT, DEP, DRA]
   INSPIRE species 19 [RAIN, TEMP, TEXT, PH, DRA, LIG, KTMP, USE]
   FAO For. Paper 77 pp 48
